433
00:21:37,219 --> 00:21:39,907
Max e Isabel,
dois dos nossos suspeitos.

434
00:21:40,876 --> 00:21:43,576
O rei do baile
e a gostosona.

435
00:21:43,578 --> 00:21:44,978
